<normalizedToken id="FFD858F5AAACA117AE28F5C74070BDBE" originalValue="“52”">&quot;52&quot;</normalizedToken>
/ &quot;Lectotype Clivina pallipes Dej. Des. S.W. Nichols 1984&quot;/ printed in red paper 
<normalizedToken id="C86100529F135AA0371A64A4714AC882" originalValue="“lectotype”">&quot;lectotype&quot;</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D4DA182A191EFD420E4293BA994C5769" pageId="28" pageNumber="47">
